            <div class="title">
                Clause 16â€”(Increase In Initial Allowances, Etc, In Respect Of Machinery Or Plant)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1949-06-23/debates/d5e2af03-f4ab-47ab-ba05-91ed70f8bb10/Clause18%E2%80%94(AnnualAllowancesEtcForOverseasMineralRights)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
