        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-65a3c458-6796-4f6e-808d-bef22edc6d80'>
            
<p class="">Amendment negatived.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
