    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">It may shorten our labours on this Amendment if I indicate straight away that, on behalf of the Government, I have very much pleasure in accepting it.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-02f5906e-227f-4ebc-b2c6-af2ea2423e31" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-06-23/debates/0005e765-474d-4309-ae76-99a2b46d6f30/Clause16%E2%80%94(IncreaseInInitialAllowancesEtcInRespectOfMachineryOrPlant)#contribution-02f5906e-227f-4ebc-b2c6-af2ea2423e31">
